ly.\n\n3.  **Input Validation:** Strict input validation on the backend (FastAPI) to prevent injection attacks and ensure data integrity before writing to the database.\n\n### Hosting & Infrastructure\n\n*   **MVP (Cost-Efficient):**\n    *   **Frontend:** Vercel (Free Tier).\n    *   **Backend/API:** AWS Lambda + API Gateway (pay-per-use model is ideal for low-volume startups).\n    *   **Database:** AWS RDS (PostgreSQL, utilizing the Free Tier or minimal instance size).\n    *   **Storage:** AWS S3 (for raw, large measurement files).\n\n*   **Scaling Path:** As usage grows, migrate the API from pure Lambda to containerized services (AWS ECS/EKS) for more predictable costs and better control over resource allocation.\n\n### Compliance (Mathakut)\n\n*   **Data Privacy (Mathakut Compliance):**\n    *   **Data Minimization:** Only collect data strictly necessary for the measurement and service provision.\n    *   **Consent Management:** Implement clear, auditable mechanisms for user consent regarding data collection and processing.\n    *   **Data Subject Rights:** Design the system to allow users to easily request access, modification, or deletion of their personal data (Right to Erasure).\n    *   **Data Residency:** Ensure data storage locations comply with the data residency requirements specified by Mathakut regulations."}, 'id': 'JofocmuFNVkUaAD6BRSM1obvyVhj00x5', 'type': 'tool_call'}]
